ve in Sr2RuO4 remains unresolved, suggesting the need to\nconsider either significant modifications to the standard chiral p-wave models\nor possible alternative pairing symmetries. Recent ideas along these lines are\ndiscussed.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 10 Oct 2012 17:51:16 GMT"}],"update_date":"2012-10-11"}
