 entanglement measures and obtain several new\nresults on these, too.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 11 Oct 2012 11:35:20 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 15 Oct 2012 17:44:44 GMT"}],"update_date":"2014-02-19"}
