 a crucial role in shaping the World Trade Web binary\nstructure and that the information encoded into the reciprocity is far more\nuseful in explaining the observed patterns.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 11 Oct 2012 15:23:57 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 12 Oct 2012 15:46:48 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-09"}
